WFMY -- We've got all the college and pro football action on our channel this weekend. Georgia takes on Tennessee in a big SEC matchup on Saturday. And on Sunday, it's a doubleheader for week five NFL as the Rams take on the Packers and Patriots face off with the Cowboys. Check out the lineup...
